{"title":"Joycon2手柄如何连接电脑测试按键摇杆等功能","slug":"Joycon2手柄如何连接电脑测试按键摇杆等功能","date":"2026-01-08T03:53:28.000Z","updated":"2026-01-09T00:50:52.126Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Joycon2手柄如何连接电脑测试按键摇杆等功能.json","excerpt":" [Figure] 测试Joycon2按键,摇杆, 以及joycon2当鼠标用; 任天堂Switch2 Joycon2 肩键失灵&#x2F;不识别&#x2F;按键卡滞&#x2F;摔坏&#x2F;按键不识别等修复, 可闲鱼搜索: 手柄一修哥","covers":["https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2026/01/08/695f2d00c2a59.png","https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2026/01/08/695f2d3cc3447.png","https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2026/01/08/695fb6c75d8b6.png"],"content":"<img class=\"lozad\" data-src=\"https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2026/01/08/695f2d00c2a59.png\">\n\n<p>测试Joycon2按键,摇杆, 以及joycon2当鼠标用; 任天堂Switch2 Joycon2 肩键失灵&#x2F;不识别&#x2F;按键卡滞&#x2F;摔坏&#x2F;按键不识别等修复, 可闲鱼搜索: 手柄一修哥</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<div> \n<button onclick=\"synthesizeSpeech()\">朗读全文</button>\n</div>\n<audio controls id=\"audioPlayer\">Your browser does not support the audio element.</audio>      \n<script>\n  function synthesizeSpeech() { \n    var inputText = document.getElementsByClassName('post-block')[0].innerText;\n    var voice = \"ZH\";\n    var url = 'https://tts.carlzeng.com:3/speech?text=' + encodeURIComponent(inputText.substring(0,3000)) + '&voice=' + voice;\n    var audioPlayer = document.getElementById('audioPlayer');          \n    audioPlayer.src = url;\n    audioPlayer.load();\n    audioPlayer.play();\n  }\n</script>\n\n\n<h1 id=\"有什么用\"><a href=\"#有什么用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"有什么用\"></a>有什么用</h1><p>让我们可以临时测试Joycon2手柄; 在脱离Switch2主机的情况下.</p>\n<p>话说Joycon2宣传的可以当鼠标</p>\n<p>项目地址: <a href=\"https://github.com/seitanmen/Joycon2forMac\">https://github.com/seitanmen/Joycon2forMac</a></p>\n<p>适用Mac和Windows电脑</p>\n<h1 id=\"怎么用\"><a href=\"#怎么用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"怎么用\"></a>怎么用</h1><p>MAC电脑连接Joycon2, </p>\n<p>通过蓝牙搜索的方式匹配两个设备; </p>\n<p>然后Mac电脑的运行编译好的可执行文件, </p>\n<p>即可捕获Joycon2的各类事件(按钮点击, 摇杆拨动, 鼠标光标移动, 重力感应, 加速度感应数据等)</p>\n<h1 id=\"相关内容\"><a href=\"#相关内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"相关内容\"></a>相关内容</